lead_paragraph: Chantel Osahor had the first triple-double in Washington history and the 15th-ranked Huskies crushed Idaho 105-53 on Tuesday night in a game that set the NCAA women's record for 3-point attempts.

headline.print_headline: Triple-Double, NCAA Mark in No. 15 Washington Women Victory
